OL,7,FRiver campaigners in Wales have hit
OL,8,Fout at the practice of spreading
OL,9,Fwaste from sewage treatment works on
OL,10,Ffarmland, warning that a lack of
OL,11,Foversight means it risks further
OL,12,Fdamaging polluted rivers.
OL,14,FThey warned that many of Wales's
OL,15,Fwatercourses were already saturated
OL,16,Fwith nutrients and that the human
OL,17,Fwaste was likely to be contaminated
OL,18,Fwith "forever chemicals",
OL,19,Fmicroplastics and pharmaceuticals.
